      • tryToSchedule

        public void tryToSchedule(Map<ExecutorDetails,String> execToComp,
                          RasNode node,
                          WorkerSlot workerSlot)

        Assign executor to worker and node. TODO: tryToSchedule is a misnomer, since it always schedules. Assignment validity check is done before the call to tryToSchedule().

        Parameters:
        execToComp - Mapping from executor to component name.
        node - RasNode on which to schedule.
        workerSlot - WorkerSlot on which to schedule.
